profile:
Back in 2016, we knew we needed our mini split heat pump cleaned…

It had obvious signs of mold. We called around and were told repeatedly by companies throughout Halifax and Nova Scotia that, outside of a filter cleaning, a full heat pump cleaning was not required.

We were not satisfied with that response. In 2016, we created our own proprietary heat pump cleaning company. Breathe Clean. Breathe Clean is Nova Scotia and North America’s first dedicated heat pump cleaning company.
